000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"689cceb5263ad970d30c77b5f11ebe73e7d28fc7","tid":978260,"uid":180385,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"9de5f72e2bab4e1c991a729a48cab185495525c2","tid":978260,"uid":93136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-11T18:56:07.000Z","msg":"點解要-1次方"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-01-11T19:04:31.000Z","msg":"Pick one point as the first one from the n points and place it anywhere on the circle, with prob = 1.<br />\nDefine the semicircle starting from the first point clockwise. Place the remaining (n-1) points on the edge of the semicircle, with prob = 1/2^(n-1)<br />\nThere are nC1 ways to pick any one point as the first point. -&gt; All points on the same semicircle = n*(1/2)^(n-1), hence ans to part b = 1 - n*(1/2)^(n-1)"},{"pid":"ef3f0765c8d9f1832b69d007645a48e3ac0bce97","tid":978260,"uid":88304,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-11T19:06:35.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"83bfafdf769153019a5822263e2d1e89660c3892","tid":978260,"uid":93136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"689cceb5263ad970d30c77b5f11ebe73e7d28fc7","tid":978260,"uid":180385,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"9de5f72e2bab4e1c991a729a48cab185495525c2","tid":978260,"uid":93136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-11T18:56:07.000Z","msg":"點解要-1次方"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-01-11T19:04:31.000Z","msg":"Pick one point as the first one from the n points and place it anywhere on the circle, with prob = 1.<br />\nDefine the semicircle starting from the first point clockwise. Place the remaining (n-1) points on the edge of the semicircle, with prob = 1/2^(n-1)<br />\nThere are nC1 ways to pick any one point as the first point. -&gt; All points on the same semicircle = n*(1/2)^(n-1), hence ans to part b = 1 - n*(1/2)^(n-1)"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-11T19:09:15.000Z","msg":"清晰"},{"pid":"bc42cc2b815583460ea81e9aaa719acf7506667f","tid":978260,"uid":93136,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"ef3f0765c8d9f1832b69d007645a48e3ac0bce97","tid":978260,"uid":88304,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"689cceb5263ad970d30c77b5f11ebe73e7d28fc7","tid":978260,"uid":180385,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"9de5f72e2bab4e1c991a729a48cab185495525c2","tid":978260,"uid":93136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-11T18:56:07.000Z","msg":"點解要-1次方"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-01-11T19:04:31.000Z","msg":"Pick one point as the first one from the n points and place it anywhere on the circle, with prob = 1.<br />\nDefine the semicircle starting from the first point clockwise. Place the remaining (n-1) points on the edge of the semicircle, with prob = 1/2^(n-1)<br />\nThere are nC1 ways to pick any one point as the first point. -&gt; All points on the same semicircle = n*(1/2)^(n-1), hence ans to part b = 1 - n*(1/2)^(n-1)"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-11T19:06:35.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-11T19:10:35.000Z","msg":"你代2睇睇 答案已經明顯錯<br />\n2點 prob 都一定係一"},{"pid":"db3088ac7dc36d5d6664606cd89b91ae04f68d4b","tid":978260,"uid":88304,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-11T19:16:20.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0e0acc90a4832248047b990e120b66984fc2438b","tid":978260,"uid":180385,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ef3f0765c8d9f1832b69d007645a48e3ac0bce97","tid":978260,"uid":88304,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"689cceb5263ad970d30c77b5f11ebe73e7d28fc7","tid":978260,"uid":180385,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"9de5f72e2bab4e1c991a729a48cab185495525c2","tid":978260,"uid":93136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-11T18:56:07.000Z","msg":"點解要-1次方"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-01-11T19:04:31.000Z","msg":"Pick one point as the first one from the n points and place it anywhere on the circle, with prob = 1.<br />\nDefine the semicircle starting from the first point clockwise. Place the remaining (n-1) points on the edge of the semicircle, with prob = 1/2^(n-1)<br />\nThere are nC1 ways to pick any one point as the first point. -&gt; All points on the same semicircle = n*(1/2)^(n-1), hence ans to part b = 1 - n*(1/2)^(n-1)"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-11T19:06:35.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-11T19:19:56.000Z","msg":"我估你係將個圓形分2份  然後放D點落去  第一點就任放其中一邊, 其他就1/2機會. 就會有(1/2)^(n-1)<br />\n但再諗深一層,  如果個圓形係分成4份, 左上,左下,右上,右下,  你個計法就應該係假設D點落晒係右上右下 / 左上左下. 但其實D點落晒係左下右下都會令個event發生.  而將個圓形分4份既話, 再諗深一層去到分8份都會有咁既問題.  所以咁諗應該唔work"},{"pid":"f487f0d98f3859ddf8976f000391ac7aad9fcedc","tid":978260,"uid":203645,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-11T19:56:47.000Z","msg":"第一點求其放,然後同佢對面果點連起黎將圓形分成兩半<br />\n第二點都係arbitrary,因為放上半又得,放下半你都可以將個圖reflect番黎睇都相等放左係上半<br />\n於是重點只係淨番既點有冇至少一點係另一半度<br />\nP(包圓心)=1-P(全部同一邊)=1-(1/2)^(n-2)"},{"pid":"da9aca2008f676c570c4ad1b25e96e9c7966dab5","tid":978260,"uid":93136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f487f0d98f3859ddf8976f000391ac7aad9fcedc","tid":978260,"uid":203645,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-11T19:56:47.000Z","msg":"第一點求其放,然後同佢對面果點連起黎將圓形分成兩半<br />\n第二點都係arbitrary,因為放上半又得,放下半你都可以將個圖reflect番黎睇都相等放左係上半<br />\n於是重點只係淨番既點有冇至少一點係另一半度<br />\nP(包圓心)=1-P(全部同一邊)=1-(1/2)^(n-2)"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-11T20:09:45.000Z","msg":"N係1點？"},{"pid":"93f824149a43ccd4d02d62d8431b0b72eb75fe06","tid":978260,"uid":3981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-11T20:15:26.000Z","msg":"putnam competition<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e892c6ecddc5966c8f8bc99ac39f8ea3b119639d","tid":978260,"uid":52817,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-11T23:56:38.000Z","msg":"邊個負皮我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3747565b6a0eafa6c9a8e69f0a4a04602b6463